						               													<description>Slovansk&amp;yacute; Opij&amp;aacute;&amp;scaron; is party board game for 4-12 players, where nobody will be sober after this game.&amp;#10; You move your figure on the board by rolling dice and try to get the figure to the square marked with its color and the arrow pointing to castle. Whoever gets there first wins the game.&amp;#10;But this will not be so easy. There are several squares on the board in different places where you have to draw a card.  The card describes some task that you need to do. If you successfully complete the task, you do not need to drink, otherwise you must drink one shot. You must drink one shot even if the other player moves his figure to the square where your piece is already standing.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes:&amp;#10;- 1 board game &amp;#10;- 6 figures&amp;#10;- 74 cards&amp;#10;- 1 dice&amp;#10;- 6 plastic shot glasses&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
